***************************************************
**                 NEWS                          **
**       News for Package \pkg{lbreg}            **
**  https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=lbreg     **
***************************************************


Changes in version 1.3 (December 2019)

o  Some help pages updated. 
o  Computation of vcov in lbreg.fit fixed for case r >= p. 
o  Bug fixed following lbreg check on 2019-12-12 19:50:57 CET -  see lbreg results.
o  NEWS added.

Changes in version 1.2 (January 2018)

o Functionality for grouped data added.  Previous versions did not handle grouped data. 

Changes in versions prior to 1.1 (2017)
  
o  Datasets added to package. 
o  Bug in 'predict.lbreg' fixed.
o  'predict.lbreg' added to package.
o  Function 'relrisk' added to package. 
o  Package made available through author's website following publication of
   Andrade BB, Andrade JML, (2018) 
   Some results for maximum likelihood estimation of adjusted relative risks, 
   \emph{Communications in Statistics - Theory and Methods}, 
   https://doi.org/10.1080/03610926.2017.1402045   
 
